3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/9bed1c4ca956a17a_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#何炅因欧阳娜娜演技被黑气愤#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【#何炅因欧阳娜娜演技被黑气愤#：欧阳娜娜反而是最会演的那个】@何炅 在节目中，为@歐陽娜娜Nana 之前被网友众嘲的表演辩解，称欧阳娜娜在节目中的表演并不是她自己对角色的理解，表演语气也不像她，是导师不负责任的指导和节目组给欧阳娜娜的设定才导致欧阳娜娜演技被黑。你认为节目中艺人表演演技差 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/7b0d3191d3f8d556_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot04\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/7b0d3191d3f8d556_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/wx2.sinaimg.cn\/crop.0.4.1280.711\/ed97c81bly1gf64v6a24kj20zk0k0adk.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/7b0d3191d3f8d556_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">陈芊芊人设<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【赵露思 丁禹兮《#传闻中的陈芊芊#》第19集抢先看！——煮饭怎么这么难！！[哈哈][哈哈]韩烁怒掀芊芊被子，芊芊惶恐：“我都这样了，你还想着生米煮成熟饭，你禽兽啊！！”[笑cry][笑cry][笑cry]】\n芊芊现在好主动，抓韩烁衣角：“你不要留我一个人嘛，你陪陪我……”  #陈芊芊人设#  ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/5571e9ce20dd7352_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot05\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/5571e9ce20dd7352_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/6a5ce645ly1gf62m3wqydj20is0et0tl.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/5571e9ce20dd7352_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#圆明园遗址公园悼念何鸿燊#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【#圆明园遗址公园悼念何鸿燊#[伤心]】2020年5月26日，港澳知名爱国企业家#何鸿燊去世#， @圆明